WEBVTT

00:00:02.627 --> 00:00:04.291
TAPE NUMBER FOUR,

00:00:05.327 --> 00:00:10.350
AN INTERVIEW WITH DAVID HERSKOWITZ, AUGUST TWENTIETH, NINETEEN NINETY SIX.

00:00:12.027 --> 00:00:13.995
in ersht MISTER Hershkovits,

00:00:14.322 --> 00:00:22.921
ir hot dertsoygn ayer kinder, ir hot, ayer zun iz adurkh gegangen ale di di shuln, mit ale di di SCHOLSRSHIPS un alts,

00:00:23.063 --> 00:00:24.899
un ayer tokhter iz,

00:00:24.899 --> 00:00:26.384
un vos iz haynt?

00:00:26.493 --> 00:00:27.022
yo.

00:00:28.092 --> 00:00:31.933
mayn zun hot gelernt in di yeshives in Khofets Khaim,

00:00:32.174 --> 00:00:33.839
in di Vest Zayt.

00:00:35.196 --> 00:00:38.525
dort in di yeshive Khofets Khaim hot er gehat

00:00:38.525 --> 00:00:41.732
zeyer a balibtn a rebe,

00:00:41.732 --> 00:00:43.863
a rosh yeshive heyst es,

00:00:44.258 --> 00:00:46.277
vos hot im zeyer zeyer lib gehat.

00:00:47.312 --> 00:00:49.233
un dan, fun dort

00:00:49.233 --> 00:00:51.140
zenen zey gegangen lernen

00:00:51.140 --> 00:00:53.552
oykh Khofets Khaim, far di gresere,

00:00:53.552 --> 00:00:55.203
hot men geshikt lernen

00:00:55.480 --> 00:00:58.764
in Tolme, deys iz nisht vayt fun Monsi.

00:00:59.192 --> 00:01:01.008
SALT dos,

00:01:01.015 --> 00:01:02.865
Spring Vali, in yene gegnt.

00:01:03.950 --> 00:01:06.175
der rosh yeshive, Rav Goldman,

00:01:06.175 --> 00:01:07.522
azoy iz geven zayn nomen,

00:01:07.815 --> 00:01:11.179
iz gegangen vayter lernen mit di groyse bo- bokherim

00:01:11.179 --> 00:01:12.400
nokh Tolme.

00:01:12.844 --> 00:01:15.116
dos iz alts mitn yeshive Khofets Khaim.

00:01:16.371 --> 00:01:17.917
der Rav Tolme

00:01:17.991 --> 00:01:22.153
hot gehat tsvey shiurim.

00:01:22.817 --> 00:01:26.152
far mitog hot er gelernt in Khofets Khaim in Tolme,

00:01:26.344 --> 00:01:30.118
in nokh mitog hot er gelernt UNK mit groyse bokherim

00:01:30.158 --> 00:01:32.649
in Yesh- in Yeshive Yuniversiti.

00:01:34.073 --> 00:01:37.459
mayn zun hot gehat a khaver, eyner Yosl Rider,

00:01:37.853 --> 00:01:40.884
vos zayne eltern hobn oykhet gevolt er zol geyn in COLLEGE.

00:01:41.397 --> 00:01:47.027
un ikh, azoy vi mayn zun hot gevunen, in di in di HIGH SCHOOL hot er gevunen SCHOLARSHIP un dos,

00:01:47.202 --> 00:01:49.778
hob oykhet gevolt er zol geyn in COLLEGE.

00:01:51.032 --> 00:01:54.699
un un hot men opgeshmuest

00:01:54.699 --> 00:01:56.814
az m'vet zey koyfn a kar,

00:01:57.208 --> 00:02:01.432
un zey veln yedn nokh mitog, nokhn lernen in Tolme, araynkumen

00:02:01.432 --> 00:02:03.010
un zey veln geyn in COLLEGE

00:02:03.010 --> 00:02:05.690
in in in Nyu York,

00:02:06.540 --> 00:02:09.183
NE- NEW YORK UNIVERSITY COLLEGE.

00:02:10.962 --> 00:02:13.588
un zey hobn ongehoybn tsu lernen a vokh tsayt,

00:02:14.016 --> 00:02:15.360
iz gekumen

00:02:15.602 --> 00:02:17.818
der rosh yeshive fun Spring Vali,

00:02:17.818 --> 00:02:19.528
un er hot gezogt, "bokherim,

00:02:19.618 --> 00:02:22.762
ikh vil nisht hobn do keyn COLLEGE bo- bokherim.

00:02:22.762 --> 00:02:24.962
ikh vil nisht az di yeshive zol heysn

00:02:24.985 --> 00:02:27.729
s'iz a yeshive vos me, fun COLLEGE.

00:02:27.887 --> 00:02:29.960
ikh vol es zol mir heysn als a yeshive

00:02:29.960 --> 00:02:32.656
vu m'lernt nor yidishe zakhn.

00:02:33.473 --> 00:02:35.486
un oyb ir vilt geyn in COLLEGE,

00:02:35.486 --> 00:02:38.262
tort ir nisht lernen, kent ir do nisht lernen vayter.

00:02:38.262 --> 00:02:40.098
geyts in andere yeshives,

00:02:40.425 --> 00:02:43.186
Mesivte, oder andere, vayter."

00:02:43.969 --> 00:02:47.135
mayn zun hot ober zeyer lib gehat dem Rav Goldman,

00:02:47.800 --> 00:02:51.523
un er iz aheymgekumen un er hot geveynt un er hot gezogt, "tati,

00:02:51.647 --> 00:02:54.082
ikh gey ikh gey nisht avekgeyn fun Goldman,

00:02:54.082 --> 00:02:55.809
ikh vil nor bayn im lernen."

00:02:56.153 --> 00:03:00.900
m'hot geredt mit dem Rav Goldman, vos m'ken dort tun. zogt im tut es oykh layd,

00:03:00.900 --> 00:03:02.596
vayl er ken oykh nisht andersh.

00:03:02.596 --> 00:03:05.186
fun dem gehalt vos er bakumt nokh fun Spring Vali,

00:03:05.186 --> 00:03:07.587
iz tsu veynik far im tsu makhn parnose,

00:03:07.645 --> 00:03:10.080
un er darf hobn di Yeshive Yuniversiti.

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:14.838
azoy vi az di kinder zenen arayngekumen mit zeyer kar, iz er eybik oykh mit gekumen mit zey

00:03:14.838 --> 00:03:17.308
un er hot gelernt in di COLLEGE.

00:03:18.580 --> 00:03:26.369
iz vos ken men tun, hot men im gefregt. zogt er, er veyst oykh nisht, ⟨s'iz⟩ s'iz di lage ⟨ot s'iz⟩ zeyer shver, ⟨far shver gevorn⟩.

00:03:27.405 --> 00:03:30.082
dort iz geven der Yosl dos,

00:03:30.713 --> 00:03:32.816
der Rider,

00:03:32.991 --> 00:03:36.680
zayn foter iz geven, iz an oysher, iz nokh haynt oykh a groyse oysher,

00:03:37.277 --> 00:03:41.062
hot er gefregt der Rav Goldman, zogst mir, vifl bakumt ir gehalt

00:03:41.062 --> 00:03:43.211
dort in in Spring Vali,

00:03:43.285 --> 00:03:44.781
vos dos?

00:03:44.989 --> 00:03:46.074
zogt er,

00:03:46.074 --> 00:03:49.438
umgefer hundert, hundert fuftsik dolar tsi a vokh.

00:03:50.592 --> 00:03:53.370
zogt er, ven m'zol aykh gebn di hundert fuftsik do,

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:56.576
vet ir geblibn do lernen mit zey dos?

00:03:56.987 --> 00:04:00.170
zogt er, ikh vel aykh zogn biz a por tog antvort.

00:04:00.666 --> 00:04:04.507
un er iz gegangen, er hot gezogt far der rosh yeshive dort fun Spring Vali,

00:04:04.547 --> 00:04:07.995
ir zolt visn, fun eyn fun do ken ikh nisht makhn keyn parnose,

00:04:07.995 --> 00:04:09.992
un ikh bin dar aroys tsu geyn,

00:04:10.403 --> 00:04:14.852
ikh ken bakumen di hundert fuftsik dolar dort un nokh dem hob ikh nokh mitog vu ikh ken lernen.

00:04:16.089 --> 00:04:19.154
zey UNK zenen nisht geven tsufridn vi der Rav Goldman geyt avek,

00:04:19.430 --> 00:04:21.449
ober zey hobn dokh nisht gehat keyn breyre.

00:04:21.777 --> 00:04:27.274
alzo, der Rav Goldman hot opgeCALLt dem Rider un er hot gezogt, az ikh vel bakumen di hundert fuftsik dolar

00:04:27.274 --> 00:04:28.841
do a vokh,

00:04:29.016 --> 00:04:30.933
bin ikh, blayb ikh do.

00:04:31.564 --> 00:04:35.827
er CALLt mikh op der Rider, er zogt, her oys, di geshikhte hot zikh a bisl farbesert,

00:04:36.424 --> 00:04:38.341
hundert fuftsik dolar vil er hobn.

00:04:38.702 --> 00:04:43.927
ikh gib hundert du bist bist deye tsu gebn fuftsik dolar? in yene tsayt iz geven fuftsik dolar

00:04:44.187 --> 00:04:45.075
a sakh gelt.

00:04:45.503 --> 00:04:47.719
hob ikh gezogt, ikh hob dokh nisht keyn breyre.

00:04:47.719 --> 00:04:49.159
ikh muz gebn fuftsik dolar.

00:04:49.350 --> 00:04:52.094
zenen ibergeblibn tsvey bokherim mitn rosh yeshive.

00:04:52.506 --> 00:04:53.968
iz men gegangen

00:04:54.025 --> 00:04:55.152
tsu eynem

00:04:55.152 --> 00:04:57.295
Vash- er hot gevoynt in di Bronks,

00:04:57.295 --> 00:04:59.540
nisht vayt fun Vashington Hayts nokh di brik.

00:04:59.540 --> 00:05:00.482
bakant dort?

00:05:01.298 --> 00:05:04.009
hot er, hot men im gefregt dort,

00:05:04.318 --> 00:05:09.273
Rav Buk, ir vet gekent gebn dos plats, ayer besmedresh tsu lernen far dos?

00:05:09.415 --> 00:05:11.906
zogt er, oyf tsu lernen? zikher! zogt er.

00:05:12.098 --> 00:05:16.845
glaykh der Rav Goldman, un mayn zun un dem Shloyme Rider's zun, der Yosl,

00:05:16.845 --> 00:05:19.652
zenen aribergegangen in der fri nayn a zeyger,

00:05:20.333 --> 00:05:31.093
un hobn gelernt dray yor fun nayn biz eyns a zeyger. der rosh yeshive hot zikh gezetst UNK tsvishn di tsvey un aroyf geleygt di hant eyner oyf dem un azoy m'hot gelernt zeyer flaysik.

00:05:31.504 --> 00:05:32.190
ir farshteyt?

00:05:32.922 --> 00:05:36.639
un nokh eyns hobn zey gegesn LUNCH un zenen gegangen in di COLLEGES.

00:05:36.639 --> 00:05:37.977
zey hobn gelernt COLLEGE.

00:05:39.115 --> 00:05:42.044
der, mayn zun,

00:05:42.270 --> 00:05:46.837
hot, vorshaynlekh hot er gut gut ales oyfgekhapt, di ale dos,

00:05:47.113 --> 00:05:49.987
un er iz alts gegangen for un for un dos.

00:05:49.987 --> 00:05:51.512
fartik gemakht COLLEGE,

00:05:51.923 --> 00:05:53.773
ven er hot fartik gemakht COLLEGE,

00:05:54.235 --> 00:05:58.481
hot men, m'hot gemakht far im a PARTY, er iz di, m'hot gemakht di shtot

00:05:58.538 --> 00:06:00.028
hot gemakht a PARTY,

00:06:00.028 --> 00:06:01.366
un m'⟨UNK⟩.

00:06:02.082 --> 00:06:04.303
un dos un m'hot im geert.

00:06:04.714 --> 00:06:08.032
un m'hot im demolts arayngeshribn, arayngeleygt in WHO'S WHO.

00:06:08.308 --> 00:06:13.553
m'iz gekumen tsun undz fregn vi azoy er iz gevezn bay di dray yor un vi azoy er iz gevezn bay di finef yor,

00:06:13.553 --> 00:06:17.381
vi azoy er iz gevezn bay di fuftsn yor un vi vi azoy er iz, vi azoy er hot geACT.

00:06:18.332 --> 00:06:19.822
a klal, s'iz,

00:06:19.822 --> 00:06:21.110
er iz gegangen

00:06:21.623 --> 00:06:26.342
vayter in COLLEGE. der Yosl Rider iz aroysgegangen funem COLLEGE.

00:06:26.415 --> 00:06:29.294
f- di urzakh, far vos er iz aroys, veys ikh nisht.

00:06:29.368 --> 00:06:31.437
oder er iz fartik gemakht COLLEGE,

00:06:32.305 --> 00:06:33.381
un dan

00:06:33.381 --> 00:06:36.011
ongehoybn tsu klern vos er zol vern, vos er zol geyn.

00:06:36.135 --> 00:06:38.474
geklert hot er koydem tsu geyn far a dokter.

00:06:38.785 --> 00:06:43.000
ober iz men gegangen, m'hot im genumen tsu vayzn epes dos, m'hot tseshnitn epes aza

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:48.381
a tsfarde, epes dos, un er hot zikh azoy fargroylt, zi hot gezogt er ken nisht geyn keyn mit dokter.

00:06:48.589 --> 00:06:50.945
iz er gegangen un er hot ongehoybn tsu lernen far LAW.

00:06:52.116 --> 00:06:55.350
geredt hot men demolts velekhs iz di beste LAW SCHOOL.

00:06:55.575 --> 00:06:58.404
hot men gezogt di groyse dos iz COLUMBIA,

00:06:58.967 --> 00:07:01.003
un s'do FORDHAM UNIVERSITY,

00:07:01.127 --> 00:07:04.153
FORDHAM UNIVERSITY iz aza gute LAW SCHOOL

00:07:04.153 --> 00:07:06.538
az der vos zey geyen aroys fun dort

00:07:07.033 --> 00:07:08.225
fun der,

00:07:08.468 --> 00:07:10.048
bakumen bald a JOB.

00:07:11.269 --> 00:07:12.225
a dos.

00:07:12.282 --> 00:07:14.267
a klal, zog ikh far mayn zun,

00:07:14.830 --> 00:07:16.835
yo er hot dos take mir dertseylt.

00:07:16.835 --> 00:07:19.076
zog ikh, gey in di FORDHAM UNIVERSITY.

00:07:19.572 --> 00:07:21.644
ober di FORDHAM UNIVERSITY iz azoy.

00:07:21.644 --> 00:07:25.556
m'darf zikh registrirn i COLUMBIA un in FORDHAM UNIVERSITY.

00:07:25.933 --> 00:07:34.466
iz azoy, tomer nemt men on dem dem UNK in ale tsvey pletser, iz dos vos er hot batsolt far der registrATION gibt men nisht tsurik.

00:07:34.759 --> 00:07:37.453
ober tomer gibt men ts-, nemt men nisht on,

00:07:37.712 --> 00:07:38.938
gibt men tsurik.

00:07:39.180 --> 00:07:43.106
dos iz der frage vu er zol zikh aynshraybn, er zol nisht shodn hobn keyn gelt.

00:07:43.483 --> 00:07:47.662
un azoy vi ikh ze az er vil azoy vi FORDHAM un UNK UNIVERSITY,

00:07:47.753 --> 00:07:48.979
COLUMBIA,

00:07:49.086 --> 00:07:51.628
zog ikh, veystu vos, shrayb dikh arayn in ale tsvey.

00:07:52.275 --> 00:07:56.251
vel'mir zen. UNK nor a epes a hundert dolar, der dos, vel'mir zen.

00:07:56.393 --> 00:07:58.077
er hot zikh geshribn ale tsvey,

00:07:58.077 --> 00:08:00.521
⟨shpits iz⟩ m'hot im ongenumen in ale tsvey pletser.

00:08:00.814 --> 00:08:04.976
azoy vi m'hot im ongenumen in tsvey pletser, hot men shoyn in COLUMBIA nisht tsurik gegebn dos gelt,

00:08:05.050 --> 00:08:05.915
iz geblibn,

00:08:05.915 --> 00:08:10.308
iz geblibn in FORD- iz er geblibn in in UNI- in FORDHAM UNIVERSITY.

00:08:10.787 --> 00:08:13.751
iz geven in FORDHAM hot zikh ongehoybn naye ts- mayses.

00:08:14.652 --> 00:08:19.489
azoy vi zayne khaveyrim hot men nisht ongenumen in FORDHAM UNIVERSITY, zenen zey geblibn in COLUMBIA,

00:08:19.950 --> 00:08:21.867
un er hot nisht gehat keyn khaveyrim

00:08:22.178 --> 00:08:23.488
do ot dos.

00:08:23.663 --> 00:08:26.829
iz dos vos er hot nisht gehat keyn khaveyrim iz nokh nisht geven azoy shlekht,

00:08:27.004 --> 00:08:28.635
nor s'gekumen vinter,

00:08:28.810 --> 00:08:32.460
un m'hot gedarft, nokh mitog hot er nisht gekent geyn in in SCHOOL,

00:08:32.460 --> 00:08:34.738
vegn fraytik tsu nakhts hot er nisht gekent geyn,

00:08:34.738 --> 00:08:37.730
un s'gekumen montik hot er nisht gevust vos m'hot gelernt fraytik.

00:08:39.828 --> 00:08:40.956
un.

00:08:40.956 --> 00:08:41.758
a klal,

00:08:41.758 --> 00:08:43.367
iz geven a mayse,

00:08:43.980 --> 00:08:46.044
az s'geven a

00:08:46.044 --> 00:08:48.356
a froy, oder a meydl, ober dos,

00:08:48.356 --> 00:08:51.669
un zi hot gezen az az er hot TROUBLE mit di zakhn,

00:08:51.692 --> 00:08:53.098
hot zi gezogt, her oys,

00:08:53.098 --> 00:08:56.326
ikh vel aropnemen vos m'lernt fraytik oyf a TAPE,

00:08:56.637 --> 00:09:00.428
un un zuntik oder montik CALL mikh op un ikh geb dir dem TAPE.

00:09:01.092 --> 00:09:03.195
un der hot geretet di situatsye.

00:09:03.420 --> 00:09:07.852
er hot aropgebakumen oyf a TAPE, ven er iz gegangen shoyn UNK iz er geven forgebreyt.

00:09:08.162 --> 00:09:09.506
azoy hot er ales gekent.

00:09:10.474 --> 00:09:12.948
un azoy vi m'hot im ongenumen azoy dos,

00:09:13.090 --> 00:09:16.898
iz eyn mol azoy zitsndik ale ineveynik azoy dos,

00:09:16.988 --> 00:09:20.627
un dort in FORDHAM iz iz a shul far galokhim gevezn.

00:09:20.734 --> 00:09:22.382
aza CATHOLIC shul.

00:09:22.793 --> 00:09:25.397
un zey zitsn azoy, s'kumt arayn a galekh,

00:09:25.397 --> 00:09:28.558
un er zet dort az mayn zun zitst mit a kapl ineveynik.

00:09:28.969 --> 00:09:33.266
vi er zet mit a kapl, geyt er tsu im tsu, zogt er, du veyst, bayn undz, zogt er, do ot iber der

00:09:33.373 --> 00:09:35.476
iber der tslomim, iber der zakhn,

00:09:35.601 --> 00:09:38.025
iz nisht sheyn tsu zitsn mit a kapl.

00:09:38.520 --> 00:09:39.436
azoy hot er gezogt.

00:09:39.436 --> 00:09:41.518
nor zogt er, du bist efsher a RABBI?

00:09:41.558 --> 00:09:42.381
fregt er im.

00:09:42.381 --> 00:09:45.719
azoy vi er hot im azoy vi geshtupt dem terets in moyl, zogt er, yo.

00:09:45.743 --> 00:09:46.642
er iz a RABBI.

00:09:46.642 --> 00:09:48.925
zogt er, demolts du megst zitsn vayter mit a kapl.

00:09:49.337 --> 00:09:50.076
zogt er.

00:09:50.076 --> 00:09:53.451
zogt er, keyner vet dir gornisht shtern, zogt er, s'iz a fraye COUNTRY, zogt er,

00:09:53.451 --> 00:09:55.169
az du b- du haltst fun dem,

00:09:55.328 --> 00:09:56.655
m'ken zitsn mit a RABBI.

00:09:58.062 --> 00:10:01.448
shoyn, un er iz geven zeyer freylekh, er ken zitsn mit a RABBI,

00:10:01.487 --> 00:10:06.375
ober di mays- nokh dem iz gekumen der, an andere galekh un er hot gezogt, dort iz do a tsimer,

00:10:06.904 --> 00:10:08.096
a tsimer, zogt er.

00:10:08.322 --> 00:10:13.817
azoy vi fun aza tip vi du bist iz nor eyner in der, tsvishn di gantse por hundert vos zenen do,

00:10:14.059 --> 00:10:16.384
tsu gebn dos tsimer far keynem ken men nisht,

00:10:16.384 --> 00:10:17.557
s'iz an iberik tsimer,

00:10:17.557 --> 00:10:19.217
mir gebn ir dir a geshank.

00:10:19.577 --> 00:10:21.309
dos tsimer kenstu dort zayn.

00:10:21.653 --> 00:10:24.397
shoyn er hot bakumen a tsimer, er hot zikh dort gekent helfn dos.

00:10:24.538 --> 00:10:26.624
iz ober faranen kinder

00:10:26.698 --> 00:10:29.155
vos zenen antisemitn oykhet azoy dos,

00:10:29.449 --> 00:10:35.990
ven er iz gegangen oyf der zayt, zenen zey ariber fun der andere zayt. zey hobn gezogt, WE DON'T LIKE THE CHOSEN CHOSEN ONE.

00:10:37.397 --> 00:10:41.073
un zey hobn dos, un er iz tsurikgekumen tsu mir, tsu tati, zogt er,

00:10:41.073 --> 00:10:44.296
ikh vet gevolt zeyer gern toyshn un tsurikgeyn in COLUMBIA.

00:10:44.296 --> 00:10:46.925
dort hobn ikh mayne khaveyrim, mayne yidn, ot dos.

00:10:47.134 --> 00:10:53.169
zog ikh, Moyshe, zog ikh, ober dokh du host host ale mol gezogt az FORDHAM UNIVERSITY iz gut antkegn a JOB shpeter un ot dos,

00:10:53.226 --> 00:10:54.876
du host shoyn gemakht tsvey yor,

00:10:54.876 --> 00:10:56.089
makh es fartik.

00:10:56.466 --> 00:10:57.686
er iz a gut kind,

00:10:57.686 --> 00:11:01.606
er hot eybik gefolgt, un er hot es fartik gemakht, iz er aroysgegangen mit di greste oystseykhenungen.

00:11:01.883 --> 00:11:03.801
un azoy vi er iz aroysgegangen,

00:11:03.807 --> 00:11:09.083
iz er, hot im der EUGENE Gold genumen far a STRICT ATTORNEY dortike hilf,

00:11:09.308 --> 00:11:10.916
un er hot dort gearbet bayn im.

00:11:10.916 --> 00:11:12.761
mit di greste oystseykhenungen.

